            "id": 6419239,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 直覺(INTU-US)大漲5.04%，報368.63美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>直覺(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTU-US</a>)截至台北時間14日03:54股價上漲17.69美元，報368.63美元，漲幅5.04%，成交量2,816,369（股），盤中最高價370.45美元、最低價352.01美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.61%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+1.01%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+1.21%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.74%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>直覺(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTU-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-16.93%</li> <li>近 1 月：-19.35%</li> <li>近 3 月：-44.77%</li> <li>近 6 月：-45.32%</li> <li>今年以來：-47.02%</li></ul></section></main>",
